ee.bpw.dhx.ws.service.impl

Class DocumentServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • ee.bpw.dhx.ws.service.impl.DocumentServiceImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentService

    @Service(value="documentService")
public class DocumentServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements DocumentService
    Class for document sending and receiving. Service is independent from capsule versions that are being sent or received, that means that no changes should be done in service if new capsule version is added.
    Author:
    Aleksei Kokarev
